Merkel Urges G-20 to Tighten Derivates Regulation

-- B y   T o n y   C z u c z k a
-- 
2011-09-27T10:14:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-27/merkel-urges-g-20-to-tighten-derivates-regulation.html
German  Chancellor Angela Merkel 
said that derivates and hedge funds need tighter regulation as
part of a package of financial market rules to help avoid any
repeat of the financial crisis.  Merkel, in a speech to a German industry federation event
in Berlin today, called on the Group of 20 to tighten derivates
regulation.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tony Czuczka in Berlin at 
